text: Suttsu District in Shiribeshi Subprefecture. is a district located in Shiribeshi Subprefecture, Hokkaido, Japan. As of 2004, the district has an estimated population of 7,316 and a density of 16.60 persons per km². The total area is 440.83 km². ==Towns== *Kuromatsunai *Suttsu Category:Districts in Hokkaido
title: Suttsu District, Hokkaido
